In a quest for the best margarita in Phoenix, my chain Mexican weary girlfriend and I stumbled in. To our delight Sean is a master mixologist/alchemist. The jalapeño margarita (off the menu) was liquid gold. The Bloody Mary was delightful. Sean made a grapefruit basil (off the menu) libation that made me forget every greyhound/salty dog I have ever had. Come and ask for Sean so that he may take his place amongst the pantheon of bartending deities.

